gurmukhi: ਜਗੰਤ ਜੋਤ ਜੁਅਾਲ ਕਾ ॥ ਛਕੰਤ ਰਾਜ ਸੁ ਪ੍ਰਭਾ ॥
transliteration: Jagadt Jot Juaal Kaa|| Chhakant Raaj Su Prabhaa||
translation: The illumination of the flame of Thy fire puzzles brightness of Thy Kingdom.

gurmukhi: ਜਗੰਤ ਜੋਤਿ ਜੈਤਸੀ ॥ ਬਦੰਤ ਕ੍ਰਿਤ ੲੀਸੁਰੀ ॥੧੨॥੨੦॥
transliteration: Jagadt Jot(i) Jaitsee|| Badant Krit Eesjree||12||20||
translation: Even Durga praises the brilliance of that conquering light.12.20.

gurmukhi: ਅਨਕਾਦ ਸਰੂਪੰ ਅਮਿਤ ਬਿਭੂਤੰ ਅਚਲ ਸਰੂਪੰ ਬਿਸੁ ਕਰਣੰ ॥
transliteration: Ankaad Daroopan Amit Bibhootan Achal Daroopan Bis(u) Karanan||
translation: He is without distress from the very beginning, Master of Unlimited wealth, an immovable Entity and Creator of the Universe.

gurmukhi: ਜਗ ਜੋਤਿ ਪ੍ਰਕਾਸੰ ਅਾਦਿ ਅਨਾਸੰ ਅਮਿਤ ਅਗਾਸੰ ਸਰਬ ਭਰਣੰ ॥
transliteration: Jag Jot(i) Prakaasan Aadh Anaasan Amit Agadsan Sarab Bharanan||
translation: There is illumination of His Light in the world; He is indestructible from the very beginning ; He, of Boundless Heaven, is the Sustainer of all.

gurmukhi: ਅਨਗੰਜ ਅਕਾਲੰ ਬਿਸੁ ਪ੍ਰਤਿਪਾਲੰ ਦੀਨ ਦਿਅਾਲੰ ਸੁਭ ਕਰਣੰ ॥
transliteration: Anadj Akaalan Bis(u) Pratipaalan Deen Diaalan Soubh Karanan||
translation: He is Invincible, Deathless, Sustainer of the Universe, Merciful Lord of the lowely and Performer of Good actions.

gurmukhi: ਅਾਨੰਦ ਸਰੂਪੰ ਅਨਹਦ ਰੂਪੰ ਅਮਿਤ ਬਿਭੂਤੰ ਤਵ ਸਰਣੰ ॥੧॥੨੧॥
transliteration: Aanand Daroopan Anhad Roopan Amit Bibhootaaag Tav Saranan||1||21||
translation: He is Blissful Entity, and Unlimited Entity of Boundless wealth, I am in Thy refuge.1.21.

gurmukhi: ਬਿਸ੍ਵੰਭਰ ਭਰਣੰ ਜਗਤ ਪ੍ਰਕਰਣੰ ਅਧਰਣ ਧਰਣੰ ਸ੍ਰਿਸਟ ਕਰੰ ॥
transliteration: Bisvanbhar Bharanan Jagad Prakaranan Adharan Dharanan Srist Karan||
translation: Thou art the Sustainer of the Universe, the Creator of the world, the Support of the helpless and the author of macrocosm.

gurmukhi: ਅਾਨੰਦ ਸਰੂਪੀ ਅਨਹਦ ਰੂਪੀ ਅਮਿਤ ਬਿਭੂਤੀ ਤੇਜ ਬਰੰ ॥
translation: Thou art Blissful and Unlimited Entity, of Unlimited wealth and of Supreme magnificence.

gurmukhi: ਅਨਖੰਡ ਪ੍ਰਤਾਪੰ ਸਭ ਜਗ ਥਾਪੰ ਅਲਖ ਅਤਾਪੰ ਬਿਸੁ ਕਰੰ ॥
transliteration: Ankhanndprataapan Sabh Jag Thaapan Alakh Ataapan Bis(u) Karan||
translation: Thy Glory is indivisible, Thou art the establisher of the whole world, Incomprehensible, without suffering and Creator of the world.

gurmukhi: ਅਦ੍ਵੈ ਅਬਿਨਾਸੀ ਤੇਜ ਪ੍ਰਕਾਸੀ ਸਰਬ ੳੁਦਾਸੀ ੲੇਕ ਹਰੰ ॥੨॥੨੨॥
translation: Thou art Non-dual, indestructible, Illuminator of Thy Light, Detached from all and the only Lord.2.22.

gurmukhi: ਅਨਖੰਡ ਅਮੰਡੰ ਤੇਜ ਪ੍ਰਚੰਡੰ ਜੋਤਿ ੳੁਦੰਡੰ ਅਮਿਤ ਮਤੰ ॥
transliteration: Ankhanndamanndan Tej Prachannddan Jot(i) Udanndan Amit Matan||
translation: Thou art indivisible, Unestablished, of Supreme Splendour and Light, and of Boundless intellect.

gurmukhi: ਅਨਭੈ ਅਨਗਾਧੰ ਅਲਖ ਅਬਾਧੰ ਬਿਸੁ ਪ੍ਰਸਾਧੰ ਅਮਿਤ ਗਤੰ ॥
transliteration: Anbhai Anaddhan Alakh Abaadhan Bis(u) Prasaadhan Amit Gadan||
translation: Thou art Fearless, Unfathomable, Incomprehensible, Unttached, Keeper of the Universe under discipline and of infinite movement.
